{{Top|leg}}
'''Cirrus Colonies Incorporated''' specialized in prefabricated buildings and construction materials for settlers and [[Scout/Legends|explorers]], likely for the use on recently colonized [[Planet/Legends|worlds]]. Many of the prefabricated buildings came equipped with their own [[Particle shield/Legends|particle shields]] to aid in hostile environments. In addition, the buildings, and the construction materials, were always extremely durable and relatively inexpensive, thus making them very effective.

